  "body": "We should update our peer management logic to prioritize maintaining peers across subnets. Each peer should publish a bitlist of persistent subnets it is subscribed to.  We want to make sure that:\n\n- We have at least one peer on each subnet\n\n- We initiate a [discovery peer search](https://github.com/PegaSysEng/teku/blob/24030e8271281e3206af900f7cba64ed079dc607/networking/p2p/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/artemis/networking/p2p/discovery/DiscoveryService.java#L28) if we canâ€™t find peers on any particular subnet\n\n",
